utilMDE
Class ICalAvailable

java.lang.Object
  utilMDE.ICalAvailable

public class ICalAvailable
extends java.lang.Object

Given one or more calendars in iCal format, produces a textual summary of available times. Run 

java mde.ICalAvailable --help
to see usage information and options.

public static java.lang.String timezone1
Time zone as an Olson timezone ID, e.g.: America/New_York. Available times are printed in this time zone. It defaults to the system time zone.
